('MagicForm AI', 'magicform-ai', 'AI-driven tool for 24/7 lead qualification and conversion.', 'MagicForm AI is an innovative AI-powered tool tailored for lead generation, designed to streamline and enhance the top-of-funnel process by qualifying, converting, and following up with leads 24/7. Targeted at businesses looking to optimize their sales processes, Magic Form simplifies the lead management journey by learning about your business, engaging with potential customers, and providing personalized follow-ups, ensuring a seamless and efficient conversion process.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/2025-01-21T17-47-56.104Z-BYwaAXTbPUMTQ5mrKbJepPPD66WuiKUjQ.PNG', 'https://www.magicform.ai/', 'freemium', '[{"plan": "Starter Plan", "price": "$49 per month", "features": []}, {"plan": "Professional Plan", "price": "$99 per month", "features": []}, {"plan": "Premium Plan", "price": "$399 per month", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"Advanced Learning Capabilities","Continuous Improvement","Customization and Integration","24/7 Availability","Scalable Solution"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
